Subject: Re: 25 frames please! (fwd)


> .mainloop
> 	while <esc is not pressed>
> 		slice 0
> 		gosub move tanks 	; simple joystuff
> 		gosub collision		; collision , 2 pages of if's then's
> 		gosub fire			; guess?
